{"tid":470743,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)回到未來1-3","createTime":"2017-11-16T14:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T19:38:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba167b86df32040884fca9b8ce8bba69185f6efd","tid":470743,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=39553b4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=af6a76d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://ste.india.com/sites/default/files/2015/01/03/309516-back-to-the-future.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fste.india.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F01%2F03%2F309516-back-to-the-future.jpg&h=44c8d741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在1985年的美國，主角馬帝&middot;麥佛萊（Marty McFly），是一個居住在加州山谷市保守家庭裏的17歲高中生，立志成為搖滾巨星。但馬帝的家庭環境並不那麼好：馬帝的父親喬治（George McFly）是個懦弱的小上班族，常受上司畢夫&middot;譚能（Biff Tannen）的刁難；母親羅蘭性格迂腐保守，看不慣任何新生事物。此時，馬帝正計畫著與女友珍妮佛（Jennifer）於週末時開家裡唯一的破車到湖邊露營...........<br />\n<br />\n2.這次，博士和馬蒂說2015年，他的兒子將發生危機，於是他們來到了科技先進的2015年。原來，馬蒂的兒子小馬蒂&middot;麥夫萊（Marty McFly Jr.）在未來即將因為與畢夫的孫子格里夫&middot;譚能（Griff Tannen）惹事生非而遭受牢獄之災，為了避免這一切，博士決定讓馬蒂化裝成小馬蒂的樣子去阻止這一切的發生<br />\n<br />\n3.在第二集的結尾，馬帝依據博士在七十年前留下的信，馬帝和1955年的博士找到了藏在礦穴中的時間機器。馬帝無意間發現在1885年的博士在寄信後不久就將被殺，於是又乘著時間機器趕往1885年。馬帝成功抵達，但油箱卻不慎破損...<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=dc847643\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6abd0cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a82c47172f978a583ab118f94ea668f2a932f23","tid":470743,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a41d5c64add75903b967027bf67b557bbaef9a1","tid":470743,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c819d29471d604af19fc0a980be159789074087","tid":470743,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4effda25c91fdc8730e7253740d811ac32c382b2","tid":470743,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":